paths: Obvious exits: north, east, south, west
description: The surrounding walls are tinted a deep black, imparting the illusion of being within the depths of a cavernous chamber.  Faintly seen along the edges of the blackness are crystalline spokes, their deep violet hue barely glimpsed in the hazy gloom.  A pulsating luminescence filters in from the north, and the faint hum of power echoes from the same source.
title: [Nexus of Elements, Earth]
